/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:43:10.000Z","msg":"所以啲港豬真係冇得救<br />\n講咁多年都仲要睇<br />\n明明中間經歷咁多野<br />\n<br />\n講劇集，劇種單一、翻炒、冇內容、冇新意、演員屎戲、演員來來去去都係果幾個、抄外國都抄得衰過人、八點懶溫馨、八半之後鬥黎鬥去<br />\n講劇集以外，個台仆街到不堪<br />\n做港共喉舌、擺埋啲大台臭架、hard sell自己野、植入式廣告、搞鳩港視，呢度大概係六年既事<br />\n尤其係新聞，一日到黑同支那打飛機、hard sell支鐵大灣區、播閪官講野、唱衰美國、開罐頭、播無關痛癢既垃圾(eg某國家有隻貓做過咩之類)<br />\n播垃圾仲要硬食，撳掣轉台又懶，好似要切佢一忽肉咁，雖然VIU同奇妙未做到TVB咁有大量劇集，但奇妙而家播港視劇又唔試下去睇<br />\n<br />\n六年都冇改變想法，難怪要睇埋翻炒溏心、翻炒宮心計啲冇水準既劇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b854a6a70d3e0ddad2165b5b862465a1da58a54d","tid":668034,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"睇奇妙好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、<br />\n星期三就播歲月留情"},{"pid":"a9c8d3a26c28044bc6e72499eea6965db7448cee","tid":668034,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇奇妙好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"